aboutSection.title: About us
aboutSection.description: We are a team of AI engineers, that build and train AI models. Our main AI model is Flaskyi, a text-to-image model that can generate images only from in-put text. In the future, we're planning to build and train more AI models like for example Flaskyi-Chat.
